  <h2 aria-level="2" role="heading">Share your voter registration tool!</h2>

  
  <p>
  If you aren't embedding your voter registration tool in a website, blog or other platform, 
  you can always promote your voter registration tool by linking to it in another way.
  </p>
  
  <h3 arial-level="3" role="heading">Share your Voter Registration tool with a button or banner.</h3>
  
  <p>
  Go to the <%= link_to "Select Button", partner_widget_image_path(@partner) %>
  page to pick a button, and then copy the code below. 
  Buttons are available in English and Spanish. 
  You can change your button at any time by repeating these steps.
  </p>
  <form class="copy_html" action="#" method="get" accept-charset="utf-8">       
    <div>
      <p><textarea name="image_link_html" readonly="readonly" rows="5" ><%= h @image_link_html %></textarea></p>        
    </div>
  </form>  

  <h3 arial-level="3" role="heading">Share links directly to your tools:</h3>
  <p>
  Use this URL to promote your Voter Registration tool: <%= link_to "https://#{RockyConf.ui_url_host}#{new_registrant_path(:partner => @partner.id)}", "https://#{request.host}#{new_registrant_path(:partner => @partner.id)}", target: "_blank" %>
  </p>
  <p>
  Use this URL to promote your Absentee Ballot Request tool: <%= link_to "https://#{RockyConf.ui_url_host}/absentee/?partner=#{@partner.id}", "https://#{request.host}/absentee/?partner=#{@partner.id}", target: "_blank" %>
  </p>
  <p>
  Use this URL to promote your Voter Status Lookup tool: <%= link_to "https://#{RockyConf.ui_url_host}/lookup/?partner=#{@partner.id}", "https://#{request.host}/lookup/?partner=#{@partner.id}", target: "_blank" %>
  </p>
  <p>
  Use this URL to promote your Pledge to Vote tool: <%= link_to "https://#{RockyConf.ui_url_host}/pledge/?partner=#{@partner.id}", "https://#{request.host}/pledge/?partner=#{@partner.id}", target: "_blank" %>
  </p>



